{
  "name": "Watch",
  "summary": "<p><strong>Watch</strong> 对象是 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Watches/Watches .htm#Watches.Watches\">Watches</a></strong> 集合的成员。</p>\n<p>使用 <strong>Watches</strong> 集合的 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Watches/Watches .htm#Watches.Add\">Add</a></strong> 方法或 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Watches/Watches .htm#Watches.Item\">Item</a></strong> 属性可返回一个 <strong>Watch</strong> 对象。</p>\n<p><b class=\"mainheaders\">示例</b></p><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例向监视窗口中添加单元格，然后在单元格 A3 中创建求和公式，并将该单元格添加至监视工具中，然后删除监视窗口中第一个单元格。ET 使用 Add 方法创建一个新的 Watch 对象。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Watches</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;B1&quot;</span>))\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Formula</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A2&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Formula</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A3&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Formula</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;=Sum(A1:A2)&quot;</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A3&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Select</span>()\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Watches</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveCell</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Watches</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Delete</span>()\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p>通过采用 <strong>Watches</strong> 集合的 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Watches/Watches .htm#Watches.Delete\">Delete</a></strong> 方法，可以从监视功能中指定删除单个单元格。</p>\n<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例向监视窗口中添加单元格，然后从“监视”窗口中删除工作簿example.xlsx的工作表 Sheet1 上的单元格 A3。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Watches</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1&quot;</span>))\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Watches</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A2&quot;</span>))\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Watches</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A3&quot;</span>))\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Watches</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Workbooks</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;example.xlsx&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Sheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A3&quot;</span>)).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Delete</span>()\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p>通过采用 <strong>Delete</strong> 集合的 <strong>Watches</strong> 方法，还可指定从“监视窗口”中删除所有的单元格。</p>\n<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例从“监视”窗口中删除所有单元格。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> i = <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>; i &lt;= <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Watches</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span>; i++) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Watches</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(i).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Delete</span>()\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
  "description": "<p>代表在重新计算工作表时跟踪的区域。<strong>Watch</strong> 对象允许用户验证其模型的准确性并调试其遇到的问题。</p>\n",
  "category": "et",
  "properties": [],
  "functions": [
    {
      "name": "Delete",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>删除对象。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例向监视窗口中添加单元格，然后删除监视窗口中第一个单元格，并显示删除后单元格的数量。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Watches</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1&quot;</span>))\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Watches</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A2&quot;</span>))\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Watches</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A3&quot;</span>))\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Watches</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Delete</span>()\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Watches</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例向监视窗口中添加单元格，然后判断如果监视窗口中单元格的数量大于1，则将监视窗口中第二个单元格删除。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Watches</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1&quot;</span>))\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Watches</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A2&quot;</span>))\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Watches</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A3&quot;</span>))\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Watches</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span> &gt; <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Watches</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Delete</span>()\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "parameters": [],
      "returns": "void"
    }
  ]
}